result.notes: Working Futures is a labour market model that provides detailed projections of UK employment by occupation and industry.  The latest set of projections relate to the period 2010 to 2020. The data is accessible at: https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/the-future-of-jobs-and-skills. For those interested in data for local areas, please contact working.futures@ukces.org.uk.
